<div class="content-page">
  <div class="content-page__inner">
    <h1 class="content-page__title">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="content-page__intro">Math Direct is designed with privacy as a core principle. We collect no personal information, require no accounts, and use no third-party tracking.</p>

    <div class="guide-section">
      <h2 class="guide-section__title">No Accounts</h2>
      <p>Math Direct does not require you to create an account, provide an email address, or share any personal information. You can use every feature of the site without identifying yourself.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="guide-section">
      <h2 class="guide-section__title">No Tracking</h2>
      <p>We do not use Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel, or any other third-party tracking tools. We do not collect usage data, behavioral data, or device fingerprints. Your activity on this site is not monitored or recorded.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="guide-section">
      <h2 class="guide-section__title">No Cookies</h2>
      <p>Math Direct does not set cookies. The only browser storage used is <strong>localStorage</strong>, which stores your lesson progress and theme preference directly on your device. This data never leaves your browser and is never transmitted to any server.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="guide-section">
      <h2 class="guide-section__title">Local Storage</h2>
      <p>Math Direct uses localStorage to save:</p>
      <ul class="guide-tips">
        <li>Lesson completion progress</li>
        <li>Student profile names</li>
        <li>Theme preference (light/dark mode)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>This data is stored entirely on your device. You can clear it at any time through your browser settings or by using the reset button on the <a href="/lessons/">Lessons page</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="guide-section">
      <h2 class="guide-section__title">Open Source</h2>
      <p>Math Direct is open-source software. You can review the entire codebase on <a href="https://github.com/jonajinga/math-direct">GitHub</a> to verify these privacy claims for yourself.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="guide-section">
      <h2 class="guide-section__title">Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, email <a href="mailto:hello@mathdirect.com">hello@mathdirect.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
